data.text:
Veronica Girard presented a book signing at the Winterset Hy-Vee recently to promote her book, “Cooking for Family, From my Nana to Your Table”. Author and entrepreneur, Girard is also a busy mother to 14-year-old Mason and baby Izabella. She has spent decades experimenting with her family’s Italian recipes and tweaking other recipes until she reached the perfect combination of […]
